bm.title: Full House at Malay BEP, Headquarter, 24th March 2009!

meta.description: FE's Malay BEPs at HQ have been attracting FULL HOUSE crowds every Tuesday night. On Tues 24th March 2009, the Malay BEP was graced by not one, not two but THREE of FE's Spokespersons, namely, Shalin Zulkifli (World Bowling Champion), Safee Sali (Malaysia's National Football Team Striker) and Wong Hong (Champion Bodybuilder). Shalin, Safee and Wong Hong shared their testimonials from using FE's Quantum Pendant with the enthusiastic audience. MC for the night is FE's ED Azizuddin Abd Malik and speakers were FE's dynamic PD Dr Mohd Fadil and Director Mat Jutawan. A BIG THANK YOU to Aziz, Dr Fadil and Mat for a great job done! SEE YOU AT THE TOP!
